Package: keystrokeR
Type: Package
Title: Plot keytrokes on a keyboard.
Version: 0.1
Author: Philipp Ottolinger [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Philipp Ottolinger <philipp@ottolinger.de>
Description: Plot the keystrokes necessary for typing an arbitrary character string. The character string gets split into single characters and is then matched to a certain keyboard layout (like QWERTY). The use of each character on the keyboard is counted and gets visualized by a fill scale.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
